HN L'a-QTShUrH YD-YHVH MHVShY'y VL'a-KBDH 'aZNV MShMV'y.
KY 'aM-'yVNThYKM HYV MBDLYM BYNKM LBYN 'aLHYKM VChT'aVThYKM HSThYUrV PhNYM MKM MShMV'y.
KY KPhYKM NG'aLV BDM V'aTShB'yVThYKM B'yVN ShPhThVThYKM DBUrV-ShQUr LShVNKM 'yVLH ThHGH.
'aYN-QUr'a BTShDQ V'aYN NShPhT B'aMVNH BTVCh 'yL-ThHV VDBUr-ShV'a HUrV 'yML VHVLYD 'aVN.
BYTShY TShPh'yVNY BQ'yV VQVUrY 'yKBYSh Y'aUrGV H'aKL MBYTShYHM YMVTh VHZVUrH ThBQ'y 'aPh'yH.
QVUrYHM L'a-YHYV LBGD VL'a YThKSV BM'yShYHM M'yShYHM M'yShY-'aVN VPh'yL ChMS BKPhYHM.
UrGLYHM LUr'y YUrTShV VYMHUrV LShPhK DM NQY MChShBVThYHM MChShBVTh 'aVN ShD VShBUr BMSLVThM.
DUrK ShLVM L'a YD'yV V'aYN MShPhT BM'yGLVThM NThYBVThYHM 'yQShV LHM KL DUrK BH L'a YD'y ShLVM.
'yL-KN UrChQ MShPhT MMNV VL'a ThShYGNV TShDQH NQVH L'aVUr VHNH-ChShK LNGHVTh B'aPhLVTh NHLK.
NGShShH K'yVUrYM QYUr VK'aYN 'yYNYM NGShShH KShLNV BTShHUrYM KNShPh B'aShMNYM KMThYM.
NHMH KDBYM KLNV VKYVNYM HGH NHGH NQVH LMShPhT V'aYN LYShV'yH UrChQH MMNV.
KY-UrBV PhSh'yYNV NGDK VChT'aVThYNV 'yNThH BNV KY-PhSh'yYNV 'aThNV V'yVNThYNV YD'yNVM.
PhSh'y VKChSh BYHVH VNSVG M'aChUr 'aLHYNV DBUr-'yShQ VSUrH HUrV VHGV MLB DBUrY-ShQUr.
VHSG 'aChVUr MShPhT VTShDQH MUrChVQ Th'yMD KY-KShLH BUrChVB 'aMTh VNKChH L'a- ThVKL LBV'a.
VThHY H'aMTh N'yDUrTh VSUr MUr'y MShThVLL VYUr'a YHVH VYUr'y B'yYNYV KY-'aYN MShPhT.
VYUr'a KY-'aYN 'aYSh VYShThVMM KY 'aYN MPhGY'y VThVSh'y LV ZUr'yV VTShDQThV HY'a SMKThHV.
VYLBSh TShDQH KShUrYN VKVB'y YShV'yH BUr'aShV VYLBSh BGDY NQM ThLBShTh VY'yT KM'yYL QN'aH.
K'yL GMLVTh K'yL YShLM ChMH LTShUrYV GMVL L'aYBYV L'aYYM GMVL YShLM.
VYYUr'aV MM'yUrB 'aTh-ShM YHVH VMMZUrCh-ShMSh 'aTh-KBVDV KY-YBV'a KNHUr TShUr UrVCh YHVH NSSH BV.
VB'a LTShYVN GV'aL VLShBY PhSh'y BY'yQB N'aM YHVH.
V'aNY Z'aTh BUrYThY 'aVThM 'aMUr YHVH UrVChY 'aShUr 'yLYK VDBUrY 'aShUr-ShMThY BPhYK L'a-YMVShV MPhYK VMPhY ZUr'yK VMPhY ZUr'y ZUr'yK 'aMUr YHVH M'yThH V'yD- 'yVLM.
